Package com.flipkart.dao

Class FlipFitAdminDAO

java.lang.Object
com.flipkart.dao.FlipFitAdminDAO
All Implemented Interfaces:
FlipFitAdminDAOInterface
public class FlipFitAdminDAO extends Object implements FlipFitAdminDAOInterface
The FlipFitAdminDAO class provides the implementation for the data access layer responsible for performing database operations related to FlipFitAdmin functionalities. It includes operations such as registering admins, approving or rejecting gym centers and gym owners, and viewing the status of gyms and gym owners.

This class uses SQL queries defined in the FlipFitConstants class to interact with the database.
